---
title: BBQ-Glazed Beef Meatballs with Garlic Veggie Mash & Charred Corn Slaw
description: A classic BBQ sauce is a wonderful topping to add, but we’re being a bit tricky tonight. Surprise everyone by using the BBQ sauce as a glaze for the beef meatballs. The smokey flavours will sing in the pan. The surprises don’t stop there because we’re making a veggie smash with parsnip and potato, a one-up from the beloved mash potato.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
